## New layout patterns introduced this session

- **Two-column comparison table** (presence-over-performance) — performance vs. presence header row + data rows
- **Numbered shift grid** (presence-over-performance) — large serif number + name + body, 2-col
- **Notes tag cloud** (presence-over-performance) — highlighted core vs. supporting tags
- **NoteEntry[] loop** (classic-notes-reimagined) — typed array rendered in a loop, optional facet/pullquote/picks per entry
- **Rule badge list** (skin-scents) — "Rule" amber badge + rule name + body, similar to Pitfalls pattern
- **Benchmark table with right-aligned column** (skin-scents) — fragrance/house/angle + dependency level

